    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNo way to theme the ui2 spill indicator (`[+x]`). I personally want to grey the indicator out, like a comment.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThe spill indicator is highlighted with a custom highlight group which defaults to `Normal`, but can be overridden by a custom config or colorscheme.\n\nKinda related to #34889.",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "how about `MsgOverflow` or `Msg<something>`\n\nalthough, `MoreMsg` already exists and seems like it could be repurposed for this. let's start with that?",
